                "Trabajo con ingresos variables y necesitaba algo flexible. Ahorra Tranquilo se adapta perfecto a mi estilo de vida freelance."
              </p>

              <!-- Achievement -->
              <div class="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-success/10 border border-success/30">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-success">✨ Controla ingresos irregulares</span>
              </div>

              <!-- Usuario -->
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 pt-3 border-t border-border">
                <div class="p-0.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-success">
                  <div class="size-12 rounded-full bg-info/20 flex items-center justify-center text-info font-bold">
                    DT
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                  <span class="font-bold text-foreground text-sm">Diego Torres</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Freelancer</span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground flex items-center gap-1">
                    <svg class="size-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                      <path d="M8 16s6-5.686 6-10A6 6 0 0 0 2 6c0 4.314 6 10 6 10zm0-7a3 3 0 1 1 0-6 3 3 0 0 1 0 6z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Bucaramanga
                  </span>
